1. *Kukavica* je prestrašena ptica koja nikada neće da leti. (The *scarecrow* is a frightened bird that will never fly.)

2. *Kukavica* je često korišćena u narodnoj medicini za lečenje katarhala. (The *scarecrow* is often used in folk medicine for the treatment of catarrh.)

3. On je bio prvi koji je proglasio sebe *kukavicom*. (He was the first to proclaim himself a *scarecrow*.)

4. *Kukavice* često vrebaju svoju plen na obroncima brda. (*Scarecrows* often lie in wait for their prey on hill slopes.)

5. *Kukavicama* je lako razaznati po njihovom glasu. (*Scarecrows* are easily identified by their voice.)